OL,3,CWoman charged in connection to deaths
OL,4,Cof four paddleboarders
OL,6,FA woman from Aberavon has been charged
OL,7,Fwith gross negligence manslaughter
OL,8,Fafter the death of four people on a
OL,9,Fpaddleboarding tour.
OL,11,FNerys Bethan Lloyd, 39, from Aberavon,
OL,12,Fhas also been charged with one offence
OL,13,Funder the Health and Safety at Work
OL,14,FAct, Dyfed-Powys Police said.
