OL,3,CWoman charged in connection to deaths
OL,4,Cof four paddleboarders
OL,6,FMorgan Rogers, 24, Nicola Wheatley,
OL,7,F40, Andrea Powell, 41, and Paul
OL,8,FO'Dwyer, 42, died in the incident
OL,9,Falong the Cleddau River in
OL,10,FHaverfordwest on October 30 2021 when
OL,11,Fthe group got into trouble in the
OL,12,Ftown's weir.
OL,14,FPolice received a call at 9.02am on
OL,15,Fthat day, stating there were a number
OL,16,Fof paddleboarders in distress at the
OL,17,Fweir on the river in the centre of
OL,18,FHaverfordwest.
