OL,6,FConfirming that criminal proceedings
OL,7,Fhad begun, Dyfed Powys Police said,
OL,8,F"Following a lengthy and complex
OL,9,Finvestigation, (...) Nerys Lloyd has
OL,10,Ftoday been charged with 4 counts of
OL,11,Fgross negligence manslaughter and 1
OL,12,Fcount under the Health and Safety At
OL,13,FWork Act".
