OL,3,CWoman charged in connection to deaths
OL,4,Cof four paddleboarders
OL,6,FRosemary Ainslie, Head of the CPS
OL,7,FSpecial Crime Division, said: "We have
OL,8,Fauthorised Dyfed Powys Police to
OL,9,Fcharge Nerys Lloyd, 39, with four
OL,10,Fcounts of gross negligence
OL,11,Fmanslaughter and one health and safety
OL,12,Foffence following the deaths of four
OL,13,Fpaddleboarders in Haverfordwest,
OL,14,FPembrokeshire, in 2021.
OL,16,F"The charges relate to a commercial
OL,17,Fpaddleboarding river tour on 30
OL,18,FOctober 2021, where four of the group
OL,19,Fbecame trapped in Haverfordwest Town
OL,20,FWeir and tragically lost their lives.
